"Entities.deleteEntity (переопределение свойств зоны)"

#: ../../source/blog/2025-09-07_August_progress_report.rst:68
msgid "macOS support"
msgstr "Поддержка macOS"

#: ../../source/blog/2025-09-07_August_progress_report.rst:70
msgid ""
"With the Vulkan PR almost merged into master, Apple getting rid of OpenGL"
" isn't a blocker to our macOS support anymore. However, macOS support was"
" broken for multiple years, always was on the back burner, and we moved "
"build systems in-between, so this is a bit of a larger job. We have a "
"good amount of macOS users who are willing to test, and even some people "
"who are still running our last macOS version, eagerly waiting for a new "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Поскольку PR Vulkan почти интегрирован в основную ветку, отказ Apple от "
"OpenGL больше не будет препятствием для нашей поддержки macOS. Однако "
